text: Median white blood cell count was 15 , 750 [UNK] 10 9 cells / l ( IQR : 10 , 000 - 25 , 700 , mean : 20 , 600 [UNK] 10 9 cells / l ) , and median neutrophil percentage was 52 . 5 % ( IQR : 31 - 68 , mean : 50 . 3 % ) . X - rays showed generalized , dense , homogeneous opacification in 24 ( 20 . 3 % ) patients , interstitial syndrome in 24 ( 20 . 5 % ) , and alveolar infiltrate in 65 ( 55 . 1 % ) , without significant differences according to the pattern of infection ( viral , bacterial or mixed ) . No patient had abscess or pneumothorax , but 4 ( 3 . 4 % ) had pleural effusion .
